// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3030 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 5475fc90-9618-5930-9e6b-25bf24e14a2c

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*")
